songs.full_title: Pack Jam (Look Out for the OVC) by Jonzun Crew
songs.title: Pack Jam (Look Out for the OVC)
songs.title_with_featured: Pack Jam (Look Out for the OVC)

description.plain:
This was Jonzun Crew’s biggest single, released in 1982. It is a testament to their mastery of electro funk. The song takes a spin on Parliament-Funkadelic’s loopy sci-fi themes of Afro-futurism.

It also featured in the video game Grand Theft Auto: Vice City Stories
